Text: I'm getting a problem installing Visio Profession. It keeps me asking for the Vispro.wwvisproww.cab. Anyone else having this problem?'

@Kazamario
Same here, however, the std version did install.
I fixed Visio Professional. It is uploaded and available now.

with NEW non-banned GOLD KMS-host keys!

* 98.212.2.163 *
****************

privileges to activate Server 2012:

slmgr.vbs /skms 98.212.2.163
slmgr.vbs /ato
88

cscript "%ProgramFiles%Microsoft OfficeOffice15ospp.vbs" /setprt:1688
cscript "%ProgramFiles%Microsoft OfficeOffice15ospp.vbs" /act 
88

privileges to activate Office 2013 (x86)
